            "type": "TextBlock",
            "text": "The Contextere Advance Virtual Assistant provides AI-enabled work instruction and insights to HVAC technicians working on industrial jobsites. This assistant provides technicians with real-time work guidance by automatically extracting contextually relevant information from industrial PDF, handwriting, and other non-standard sources.",
